	<<set _cName to setup.Companion.name()>>
	<<if _cName eq "Brook">>
		@@.mc-thoughts; As you entered the room, you immediately saw her. But she wasn't alone. Fortunately, you entered just in time, and as soon as you did, the ghost let her go and vanished@@<br>
		@@.mc-speech; <<= _cName>>, are you alright? I saw what the ghost was doing to you...@@<br>
