		It seems she doesn't want to be interrupted. But as soon as the ghost saw you, it disappeared. @@<br>
		@@.mc-speech; <<= _cName>>, are you alright? I heard strange noises...@@<br>
		@@.notmc-speech; Don't worry, it just caught me by surprise.@@<br>
		@@.mc-speech; Sure...@@<br>
	<<elseif setup.Companion.isTransByName(_cName)>>
		@@.mc-thoughts; You suddenly burst into the room and see <<= _cName>> engaging in oral sex with the ghost. His movements are full of enthusiasm, but as soon as you enter, the ghost vanishes, leaving <<= _cName>> with wet lips and a face full of confusion.@@<br>
		@@.mc-speech; <<= _cName>>, what the hell is going on here?!@@<br>
