	<<= _cName>>'s sanity: - <<= setup.Companion.decreaseSanity()>><<statIcon setup.StatIcon.SANITY>><br>
	Your <<statIcon setup.StatIcon.HEARTH>> +15<br>
	<<addLust 15>>
<</widget>>

